Final Architecture

S3 Bucket (multiple CSV)
        │
        ▼
Spring Batch Job
        │
        ├── Step 1 (Tasklet)
        │        List CSV files
        │
        ├── Step 2 (Chunk)
        │        Read CSV rows
        │        Process
        │        Batch insert DB
        │
        └── Step 3 (Tasklet)
                 Move file to processed folder


